David Alan Basche https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/David_Alan_Basche 0 David Alan Basche (born August 25, 1968) is an American actor. He is the best known for playing Todd Beamer in the film United 93, directed by Paul Greengrass. He has appeared in regional and professional theater, film and television including guest appearances on numerous television dramas. David_Alan_Basche ( born August_25_,_1968 ) is an_American_actor .
